  "title": "Resident Engineer (C&S)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Resident Engineer (Residential Development)</strong></p><p>1.    Minimum 5 years’ experience as a Resident Engineer, with site experience in construction management and supervision of residential condominium developments.</p><p>2.    Experience in ERSS supervision.</p><p>3.    Experience in PBU and precast supervision. </p><p>4.    Registered with IES/ACES as a Resident Engineer.</p><p>5.    Able to lead a team of site management staff and ensure compliance with Consultants’ and Government authorities’ requirements.</p><p>6.    Good team player, with the ability to oversee and ensure\ncontractors complete defect rectification within stipulated timelines.</p><p>7.    Preferably with prior experience in semi top-down construction and high-rise developments with basement works.</p><p>8.    Preferably with experience in working with marine clay condition\nand grout mix pile.</p>",
