    "description": "<p>P &amp; T CONSULTANTS PTE. LTD.</p>\n<p>ARCHITECTURAL &amp; ENGINEERING CONSULTANCY SERVICES.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>P&amp;T Consultants Pte Ltd offers the full range of architectural and civil &amp; structural engineering services. Many prestigious projects have been undertaken, including offices, retail complexes, industrial development, private as well as public housing schemes in Singapore, China, Malaysia and other South East Asia countries.</p>\n<p>Today, the firm employs about 200 staff who have access to the P&amp;T group in support and services as well as their computer facilities. The P&amp;T group itself has a total employee strength of around 1500 staff.</p>",
